---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { SITE } from '../lib/site';
---

<BaseLayout title={`Privacy Policy | ${SITE.name}`} description="Privacy Policy for VettedPick.com">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 prose prose-gray max-w-none">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p><em>Last updated: July 1, 2026</em></p>

    <p>
      {SITE.name} ("we," "us," or "our") operates {SITE.url}. This page informs you of our policies
      regarding the collection, use, and disclosure of personal information when you use our website.
    </p>

    <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
    <p>
      We may collect anonymous usage data through standard web analytics tools, including pages
      visited, browser type, and referring URLs. We do not knowingly collect personal information
      unless you voluntarily contact us via email.
    </p>

    <h2>Cookies and Tracking</h2>
    <p>
      Our site may use cookies for basic functionality and analytics. When you click affiliate links
      to Amazon.com, Amazon may set cookies on your device according to their own privacy policy.
      We may also use third-party advertising pixels (such as Meta Pixel) if enabled for marketing
      analytics.
    </p>

    <h2>Affiliate Links</h2>
    <p>
      {SITE.name} participates in the Amazon Services LLC Associates Program. Clicking our Amazon
      links may result in cookies being placed by Amazon to track qualifying purchases. See Amazon's
      privacy policy for details on how they handle your data.
    </p>

    <h2>How We Use Information</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>To improve our website and content</li>
      <li>To respond to inquiries you send us</li>
      <li>To analyze traffic and marketing performance</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p>
      We use third-party services including Amazon (affiliate program), Cloudflare (hosting), and
      potentially Meta (advertising). Each service has its own privacy policy governing data they
      collect.
    </p>

    <h2>Your Rights</h2>
    <p>
      Depending on your location, you may have rights to access, correct, or delete personal data we
      hold. Contact us at {SITE.email} to make a request.
    </p>

    <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
    <p>
      Our site is not directed at children under 13. We do not knowingly collect information from
      children.
    </p>

    <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p>
      We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with
      an updated date.
    </p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>
      Questions about this Privacy Policy? Email us at <a href={`mailto:${SITE.email}`}>{SITE.email}</a>.
    </p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
